{"tid":825849,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【颱風山竹】石澳「情人橋」難抵風浪粉碎　郊遊拍婚照勝地成追憶","createTime":"2018-09-17T23:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T08:18:17.000Z","uid":130626,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"18330684bd9ce08ddb0f85672adea868f9a53802","tid":825849,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T23:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1871800/org/4b060509459d64f7c228cd9097b0fc07.jpg/RI2lQ209PmbGg4xB6Bd7eE4vgu6dh2IrsqcT9bKnE_U?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1871800%2Forg%2F4b060509459d64f7c228cd9097b0fc07.jpg%2FRI2lQ209PmbGg4xB6Bd7eE4vgu6dh2IrsqcT9bKnE_U%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=376fe8a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1872566/org/bfde012677672351fcc7282b600dc980.jpg/0i4SzJAQKDmqJvviPufAmk6kcGnxjdJjzvtVjs77VY4?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1872566%2Forg%2Fbfde012677672351fcc7282b600dc980.jpg%2F0i4SzJAQKDmqJvviPufAmk6kcGnxjdJjzvtVjs77VY4%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=bd5f4a7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1873228/org/23415400de455752caddd67dbb08bc62.jpg/hG-933ol5A6ImG-XEvxaAMERoWh02_KYR_K0m0fytJs?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1873228%2Forg%2F23415400de455752caddd67dbb08bc62.jpg%2FhG-933ol5A6ImG-XEvxaAMERoWh02_KYR_K0m0fytJs%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=942c1526&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n颱風「山竹」破壞力甚強，除了市區建築物受損外，一些郊遊熱點亦被摧毀。連接石澳後灘與大頭洲有的粉藍色橋有「情人橋」之稱，是不少新人拍攝婚紗照的熱點。今日（17日）有人發現整座橋已被摧毀，網民紛紛大呼惋惜。<br />\n<br />\n「情人橋」是連接石澳後灘及大頭洲的一道粉藍色小橋，相傳因橋身只夠兩人通過，加上粉藍浪漫感覺因而得名。今日中午約12時，有網民指該橋已斷裂。記者致電當地居民了解，對方亦指：「成條斷咗」。因該處是不少人拍攝婚紗照的勝地，有人直指：「好可惜」、「比番藍橋我地」，大呼無奈。<br />\n<br />\n情人橋又名「藍橋」，潮退時連接石澳後灘及大頭洲。遊人登上大頭洲的途中，可看見很多因風化而形成的奇石，亦可回頭看石澳全景。<br />\n<br />\n有石澳村民指，「藍橋」是由政府興建的，但不知道何時興建，早年有進行加固工程。去年「天鴿」吹襲都可保得住「藍橋」，今年「藍橋」受不住「山竹」的蹂躪，瓦解一地，村民對此感到無奈。"},